TEST STEPS

1. Open test case in a text editor;
2. Open the same test case in a scenario editor;
3. Change script in a text editor and save it;
4. Verify that script was changed in scenario editor;
5. Repeat vice-versa: change script in scenario editor, verify it has been changed in a text editor;
